
Material Class:
	Holds/Creates VAO
	Holds/Creates VBO
	Holds/Loads Shaders/Program
	Binds/Unbinds VAO/VBO/Shader
	Sends data to VBO
	Draws Arrays

Primitive Classes:
	Has/Is a material?
	Sets VertexAttrbi Pointers
	Enables VertexAttrib Arrays
	Sets up Uniforms?
	Sets up Texture Uniforms?
	
	Handles Primitive specific data type
	Draws (including batch vs singles?)

Emphasize Go-awesomeness
	Drawable - Anything with the draw function
	Loadable? - Has a Load(Filename)


-Primitive itself is just the struct
--Then we define the init, create, draw methods

